text: Fenerbahçe is a sports club in Istanbul, Turkey. It was officially founded in 1907. Fenerbahçe's home stadium is the Fenerbahce Şükrü Saraçoğlu Stadium in Kadıköy, Istanbul. They have won the Spor Toto Super League 19 times and Ziraat Turkish Cup 6 times. == Other websites == * Official website of Fenerbahce * Fenerbahceulker basketball website * Fenerbahce Ulker Spor * Fenerbahce Community Portal Category:Turkish football clubs
